\c 7
\s Dhaniyeri anorota zvikara zvina
\p
\v 1 Mugore rekutanga raBherishazari mambo weBhabhironi, Dhaniyeri wakaona chiroto nechiratidzo mumusoro wake pamubhedha wake. Ipapo wakanyora chiroto ndokureva dingindira radzinyaya.
\v 2 Dhaniyeri wakataura ndokuti: Ndakaona muchiratidzo changu pausiku, zvino tarira, mhepo ina dzematenga dzichibudira kugungwa guru.
\v 3 Zvikara zvina zvakakwira kubva mugungwa zvakasiyana chimwe nechimwe
\v 4 Chekutanga chaiva chakaita seshumba, uye chaiva nemapapiro egondo. Ndakatarira kusvika mapapiro acho adzurwa, zvino chikasimudzwa kubva pasi, ndokumiswa nemakumbo semunhu. moyo wemunhu ndokupiwa kwachiri.
\v 5 Zvino tarira, chimwe chikara, chechipiri, chakaita ebheya, chakazvimisa nerutivi rwumwe, chine mbabvu nhatu mumuromo macho pakati pemazino acho. Zvino vakareva seizvi kwachiri: Simuka, udye nyama zhinji.
\v 6 Shure kweizvi ndakaona, zvino tarira chimwe, seingwe yaiva nemapapiro eshiri pamusana payo, chikara chaivawo nemisoro mina, utongi ndokupiwa kwachiri.
\v 7 Shure kweizvi ndakaona muchiratidzo cheusiku, zvino tarira, chikara chechina, chinotyisa uye chinovhundusa, uye chakasimba kwazvo kwazvo. Zvino chaiva nemazino makuru edare; ndokupedza, ndokuguranya, ndokutsika-tsika zvakasara netsoka dzacho. Zvino chaiva chakasiyana nezvikara zvese zvakachitangira, uye chaiva nenyanga gumi.
\v 8 Ndikacherechedza nyanga, ndokuona, kwakabuda pakati padzo rumwe runyanga rudiki, nyanga nhatu dzekutanga dzakadzurwa nemumidzi pamberi parwo, zvino tarira, parunyanga urwu paiva nemaziso semaziso emunhu, nemuromo uchitaura zvinhu zvikuru.
\p
\v 9 Ndakatarira kusvika zvigaro zveushe zvagadzwa. Zvino kwakagara Mukuru wemazuva, zvipfeko zvake zvaiva zvakachena semagada echando, nevudzi remusoro wake rakaita semakushe akanatswa; chigaro chake cheushe chiri vira remoto, mavhiri acho ari moto unopfuta.
\v 10 Rukova rwemoto rwaiyerera rwuchibuda kubva pamberi pake, churu chezvuru chakachishumira. uye vane zvuru gumi vakapetwa kane zvuru gumi vakamira pamberi pake, mutongo wakamiswa, mabhuku ndokuzarurwa.
\v 11 Ipapo ndakatarira, nokuti inzwi remashoko awa makuru runyanga arwakataura: Ndakatarira kusvika kusvika chikara chaurawa, nemuviri wacho waparadzwa, ndokupiwa kumoto unopfuta.
\v 12 Zvino maererano nezvikara zvakasara, umambo hwazvo hwakaKana dziri dzimwe mhuka, dzakatorerwa ushe hwadzo, asi upenyu hwadzo hwakawedzerwa kusvikira nhambo nenguva zvakatenderwa.
\v 13 Ndikaona pane zvandakaratidzwa usiku, ndikaona umwe akafanana nomwanakomana womunhu achiuya namakore okudenga, akasvika kune akakwegura pamazuva ake, vakamuswededza pamberi pake.
\v 14 Akapiwa simba, nokubwinya, noushe, kuti vanhu vese namarudzi ese namarimi ese vamushumire; simba rake roushe isimba risingaperi, risingazopfuuri, uye ushe hwake haungazoparadzwi.
\p
\v 15 Kana ndirini Dhaniyeri, mweya wangu wakatambudzika mukati momuviri wangu, uye zvandakaona mumusoro mangu zvakandivhundusa.
\v 16 Ndikaswedera kune umwe akange amirepo, ndikamubvunza kududzirwa kwechokwadi kwezvinhu izvi zvese. Akandiudza, akandizivisa kududzirwa kwezvinhu izvozvi.
\v 17 Mhuka idzi huru, idzo ina, ndiwo madzimambo mana achamuka panyika.
\v 18 Asi vatsvene veWekumusoro-soro vachapiwa ushe, ushe uchava hwavo nokusingaperi-peri.
\p
\v 19 Ipapo ndakada kuziva kududzirwa kwachokwadi kwemhuka yechina, yakange yakasiyana nedzimwe dzese, yakange ichityisa zvikuru, yakange ina meso outare, nzara dzayo dziri dzendariraiyo yakange yapedzanokuputsanya, nokupwanya zvakasara netsoka dzayo;
\v 20 uye pamusoro penyanga dzine gumi dzakange dziri pamusoro wayo, norumwe runyanga rwakazobuda, dzimwe nyanga nhatu dzikaparadzwa pamberi parwo, irwo runyanga rwakange runa meso nomuromo wakange uchitaura zvikuru, rwakange rwakapfuura dzimwe shamwari dzarwo paukuru.
\v 21 Ndakatarira, ndikaona runyanga urwu ruchirwa navatsvene, nokuvakunda;
\v 22 kusvikira akakwegura pamazuva ake achisvika, vatsvene veWekumusoro-soro vakaruramisirwa, nguva ikasvika yokuti vatsvene vapiwe ushe.
\p
\v 23 Akati: Mhuka yechina bwuchava vushe hwechina panyika, bwuchasiyana noumwe ushe hwese, uchapedza nyika yese, nokuupwanya nokuuputsanya.
\v 24 Kana dziri nyanga dzine gumi, paushe uhu pachamuka madzimambo ane gumi, asi mumwezve achamuka shure kwavo; iye achasiyana navamwe vokutanga, achakunda madzimambo matatu.
\v 25 Achataura mashoko okumhura Wekumusoro-soro, uchaparadza vatsvene, uye achatsvaka mano okushandura nguva nemirairo; ivo vatsvene vachaiswa mumaoko ake kusvikira nguva imwe nedzimwe nguva, nehafu yenguva.
\v 26 Asi kutonga kuchatanga, vachabvisa simba rake, kuti varipedze nokuriparadza kusvikira pakuguma.
\v 27 Ipapo ushe nesimba noukuru hwoushe hwese pasi pedenga rese, zvichapiwa vatsvene veWekumusoro-soro; ushe hwake ndohwokusingaperi, masimba ese achamushumira nokuteerera.
\v 28 Ndiko kuguma kweshoko. Kana ndirini Dhaniyeri, pfungwa dzangu dzakandivhundusa kwazvo, chiso changu chikashandurwa mukati mangu; asi ndakachengeta shoko iri mumwoyo mangu.